ActSpecial Economic Measures Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Belarus) Regulations
PrecisRegulations amending the SPECIAL ECONOMIC MEASURES (BELARUS) in order to 1) add nineteen (19) individuals and twenty-five (25) entities to Schedule 1 of the Regulations; and 2) expand the criteria under which individuals and entities can be listed.
